You should hang out.

00:14:32.780 --> 00:14:35.990
And I had to kind of give the
caveat, when I was on my way

00:14:35.990 --> 00:14:38.090
up to the session,
like, my wife is

00:14:38.090 --> 00:14:40.797
within weeks of giving birth.

