00:30:07.230 --> 00:30:10.260
AUDIENCE: First off, thank
you so much for joining us.

00:30:10.260 --> 00:30:12.530
As one of your fans who loves
a little bit of a window

00:30:12.530 --> 00:30:15.300
into your life and the creative
process, much appreciated.

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:17.330
ANDREW MCMAHON: Thank you.

00:30:17.330 --> 00:30:19.790
AUDIENCE: You talk
about how you've

00:30:19.790 --> 00:30:22.283
been on all these different
projects and bands

00:30:22.283 --> 00:30:24.200
and you've gone through
a lot of life changes.

00:30:24.200 --> 00:30:27.810
You talked earlier about being
a 22-year-old kid who, you know,

00:30:27.810 --> 00:30:28.310
whatever.

00:30:28.310 --> 00:30:30.060
I don't care about a
sperm bank right now.

00:30:30.060 --> 00:30:31.490
Just treat me.

00:30:31.490 --> 00:30:35.630
Obviously, your creative process
